      "description": "Execute a recruitment query and return results",
      "docstring": "Execute a recruitment query and return results\n\nSupports two DSL formats:\n1. Dict format: Direct filter dictionary (simple queries)\n2. String format: Custom DSL parsed by QueryParser (advanced queries)\n\nThe dual format support enables:\n- Simple API queries using JSON filters\n- Complex queries using domain-specific language\n- Gradual migration from old to new query system\n\nCRITICAL: Soft delete filter (deleted_at IS NULL) MUST be applied in both paths\nto prevent data leakage. This is a security requirement for multi-tenant systems.",
